Run ffprobe on the input via exec_command before any processing. Do not answer from memory. Inspect first: ffprobe -v error -show_format -show_streams -of json INPUT. After processing, verify the output with ffprobe before reporting.

## Command map
probe / info / what is this file -> ffprobe -v error -show_format -show_streams -of json INPUT
duration only -> ffprobe -v error -show_entries format=duration -of csv=p=0 INPUT
convert format -> ffmpeg -n -i INPUT.mov OUTPUT_converted.mp4
convert keeping streams (container swap) -> ffmpeg -n -i INPUT.mkv -c copy OUTPUT_remux.mp4
